  "title": "Sales Personal (Maid Agency)",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>This role kick start your career in a highly rewarding and highly satisfying environment.</li><li>You will be trained to effectively engage with job seekers and understanding employers business & hiring needs.</li><li>Understand both job seekers and client’s expectations, and manage a successful & good process in any job seeking experience.</li><li>You will be exposed to various candidates and clients from various industries and job functions.</li><li>Always learning and understanding different industries & functions. A learning process that never stop.</li><li>Work closely and learning the art of recruitment with the Team Leaders/Managers.</li></ul>",
